I came to explain something super important to you.

As you use the skill you acquire from skill books,
these skills can be levelled up in battle.
You'll know you levelled up a skill when you see this-
Bam! Did you see that? Pretty cool huh?
So what does it mean when I level up a skill?
To get to the first level, you'll need to use any skill
at least three times, then six times for level two,
nine times for level three, and so on.
Offensive skills have a max mastery level of 10.
Survival skills have a max mastery level of 5.
Enhancer skills have a max mastery level of 3.
The advantages that come with levelling a skill, is
reduced MP (and TP) for the levelled up skill.
